[h1]储存网络[/h1]
[h1][i]Storage Network[/i][/h1]

为《缺氧》添加一套集中式储存与生产网络。使用专用服务器统一保存固体、液体、气体、电力及高能粒子，通过端口接入运输轨道、管道和电路，并在同一个管理面板中调度物资、规划生产、供应建筑与监控整个网络。

[i]Storage Network adds a centralized storage and production network to Oxygen Not Included. Dedicated servers store solids, liquids, gases, power, and radbolts; ports connect the network to rails, pipes, and power circuits; and a unified panel handles inventory, production planning, building supply, and network monitoring.[/i]

