[h2]主要功能 / Main Features[/h2]
[list]
[*] [b]完整的网络基础设施[/b]：建造储存网络核心，以及小型、中型和大型固体、液体、气体、电池、冷库与高能粒子服务器。
[*] [i][b]Complete network infrastructure:[/b] Build a Storage Network Core and small, medium, or large servers for solids, liquids, gases, power, refrigerated goods, and radbolts.[/i]

[*] [b]多种入网与出网端口[/b]：连接固体运输轨道、液体管道、气体管道、电路和高能粒子系统；可配置筛选、来源、目标、阈值与输出策略。
[*] [i][b]Input and output ports:[/b] Connect conveyor rails, liquid pipes, gas pipes, power circuits, and radbolt systems, with configurable filters, sources, targets, thresholds, and output policies.[/i]

[*] [b]集中式管理面板[/b]：按星球和分类查看库存、容量、内容物、运行状态及周期趋势，并直接配置已接入建筑。
[*] [i][b]Centralized management panel:[/b] Browse inventory, capacity, contents, operating status, and cycle trends by world and category, and configure enrolled buildings directly.[/i]

[*] [b]网络化生产[/b]：生产建筑可从网络请求原料，并将成品自动存回匹配的服务器；农场、发电设施及部分储存建筑也可使用网络供料或输出。
[*] [i][b]Networked production:[/b] Production buildings can request ingredients and return products to matching servers. Farms, generators, and supported storage buildings can also use network supply or output.[/i]

[*] [b]生产订单系统[/b]：使用订单生产中心和刻录盘保存制造配方，创建生产订单，追踪原料缺口、生产进度与异常状态，并自动规划多级补产链。
[*] [i][b]Production orders:[/b] Use the Order Production Center and Engraving Disks to store recipes, submit orders, track material shortages and progress, and automatically plan multi-step production chains.[/i]

[*] [b]建筑材料供应[/b]：复制人可从材料出网端口领取网络内的建造材料。
[*] [i][b]Construction supply:[/b] Duplicants can fetch construction materials from solid output ports.[/i]

[*] [b]泉直接入网[/b]：支持将已接入的泉类建筑产物直接存入匹配服务器，并可配置网络满载时的处理方式。
[*] [i][b]Direct geyser output:[/b] Enrolled geysers can send their output directly to matching servers, with configurable fallback behavior when the network is full.[/i]

[*] [b]跨星球传输[/b]：在火箭上安装储存网络中继器，使网络在火箭进入太空后具备跨星球物资传输能力。
[*] [i][b]Interplanetary transfer:[/b] Install a Storage Network Relay on a rocket to enable cross-world item transfers while the rocket is in space.[/i]

[*] [b]自动化支持[/b]：使用网络电量传感器监控总充电比例；通过自定义逻辑输出器组合库存、建筑及网络状态并输出自动化信号。
[*] [i][b]Automation support:[/b] Monitor total stored charge with the network energy sensor, or build custom logic from inventory, building, and network states and send it to automation wires.[/i]

[*] [b]便捷界面[/b]：窗口支持拖动、缩放、筛选、平滑滚动和位置记忆。
[*] [i][b]Flexible interface:[/b] Windows support dragging, resizing, filtering, smooth scrolling, and saved positions.[/i]
[/list]

[h2]使用方式 / How to Use[/h2]
[list]
[*] 研究储存网络科技并建造“储存网络核心”。
[*] [i]Research Storage Network technologies and build a Storage Network Core.[/i]

[*] 建造所需类型与容量的服务器，再用对应端口连接运输轨道、管道、电路或高能粒子系统。
[*] [i]Build servers of the required type and capacity, then connect rails, pipes, circuits, or radbolt systems with the matching ports.[/i]

[*] 选中受支持的原版建筑，通过侧屏或用户菜单将其接入网络，并配置供料、输出与筛选策略。
[*] [i]Select a supported vanilla building, enroll it through its side screen or user menu, and configure supply, output, and filter policies.[/i]

[*] 从管理菜单打开“储存网络”面板，查看库存、管理设备并创建或追踪生产订单。
[*] [i]Open the Storage Network panel from the management menu to inspect inventory, manage devices, and create or track production orders.[/i]
[/list]

[h2]重要说明 / Important Notes[/h2]
[list]
[*] 网络按星球管理；通常只有同一星球上的核心、服务器、端口和已接入建筑可以互相访问。跨星球传输需要火箭中继器。
[*] [i]Networks are world-based. Cores, servers, ports, and enrolled buildings normally access devices on the same world; cross-world transfer requires a rocket relay.[/i]

[*] 服务器需要可用的储存网络核心，端口也必须正确连接到对应的运输系统后才能工作。
[*] [i]Servers require an available Storage Network Core, and ports must be connected to the matching transport system before they can operate.[/i]

[*] 固体物品通常通过材料入网端口进入服务器；关闭固体服务器的“允许人力操作”后，复制人将不能直接从中取物。
[*] [i]Solid items normally enter servers through solid input ports. Disabling manual operation on a solid server prevents duplicants from taking items directly from it.[/i]

[*] 本模组会改变物资储存与调度方式，但不会完全取代运输轨道、管道、电路及复制人的常规物流。
[*] [i]The mod changes how resources are stored and routed, but does not completely replace rails, pipes, circuits, or normal duplicant logistics.[/i]
[/list]

