[h2]反馈 / Feedback[/h2]
如果遇到问题，请提供 [b]Player.log[/b]、简单复现步骤、当前星球及相关建筑配置；截图也会很有帮助。

[i]If you encounter a bug, please provide your [b]Player.log[/b], reproduction steps, the affected world, and the relevant building settings. Screenshots are also helpful.[/i]
